            <TextBlock Height="220" HorizontalAlignment="Left" Margin="311,12,0,0" Name="textAbout" 
                   Text="OCTGN &quot;Online Card and Tabletop Gaming Network&quot; was originally developed by jods &quot;Joel Dumas&quot;. &#13;&#13;This program allows anyone to create a game file for use in OCTGN. A game file is typically a TCG (Trading Card Game).&#13;&#13;Feel free to submit any ideas or bugs you may have. We look forward to hearing from you. Enjoy the games!" 
                   VerticalAlignment="Top" Width="199" Opacity="1" TextWrapping="Wrap" Padding="5" FontSize="12" />
